Hi, Code indentation does not work for Javascript code in a <script> block in HTML mode. Indentation works OK in .js files in javascript mode. Adding html to the javascript fileglob "*.{js,html}" forces HTML into Javascript mode, indentation works OK, but HTML is not highlighted/indented correctly. Environment: Windows XP Home SP2 java version "1.5.0_08" Java(TM) 2 Runtime Environment, Standard Edition (build 1.5.0_08-b03) Java HotSpot(TM) Client VM (build 1.5.0_08-b03, mixed mode) jEdit 4.3pre8 Thanks 